Package: nornet-api
Architecture: any
Depends: python-ipaddr,
         python-netifaces,
         rsplib-tools,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${python:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: NorNet API
 This package contains the NorNet Python API library. It contains functions
 to communicate with the central server (MyPLC), based on XMLRPC.
 .
 See http://www.nntb.no for details on NorNet!

Package: nornet-routing
Architecture: any
Depends: iputils-ping,
         iputils-tracepath,
         nornet-api,
         traceroute,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: NorNet Routing Control
 This package contains the scripts to configure the routing of NorNet
 nodes.
 .
 See http://www.nntb.no for details on NorNet!

Package: nornet-tunnelbox
Architecture: any
Depends: nornet-routing,
         python (>= 2.7),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: NorNet Tunnelbox Control
 This package contains the scripts to configure the tunnelboxes of NorNet
 sites.
 .
 See http://www.nntb.no for details on NorNet!
